We can work this out.

32:11.463 --> 32:13.327
- We...
- Listen to me!

32:14.537 --> 32:16.473
There's something you have to do.

32:18.536 --> 32:21.348
I'm gonna be going to jail for like

32:21.739 --> 32:23.705
